aluated the effectiveness of the design and", "bbox": [162.5, 913.8, 1112.5, 934.6]}, {"text": "operation of its disclosure controls and procedures as of December 31, 2004. The company’s disclosure controls", "bbox": [162.5, 938.8, 1112.3, 959.6]}, {"text": "and procedures are designed to ensure that information required to be disclosed by the company in the reports", "bbox": [162.5, 963.8, 1112.3, 984.6]}, {"text": "that are filed or submitted under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 is recorded, processed, summarized and", "bbox": [162.5, 988.8, 1112.5, 1009.6]}, {"text": "reported, within the time periods specified in the Securities and Exchange Commission’s rules and forms. Based", "bbox": [162.5, 1013.8, 1112.5, 1034.6]}, {"text": "on this evaluation, the company’s Chief Executive Officer and Chief Financial Officer have concluded that these", "bbox": [162.5, 1038.8, 1112.4, 1059.6]}, {"text": "controls and procedures are effective.", "bbox": [162.5, 1063.8, 475.9, 1084.6]}, {"text": "Management’s annual report on internal control over financial reporting. Refer to Management’s Report on", "bbox": [162.5, 1117.4, 1112.5, 1138.5]}, {"text": "Internal Control Over Financial Reporting on page 102.", "bbox": [162.5, 1142.4, 635.2, 1163.3]}, {"text": "Audit report of the independent registered public accounting firm. Refer to Report of Independent Registered", "bbox": [162.5, 1196.3, 1112.3, 1217.3]}, {"text": "Public Accounting Firm on page 103.", "bbox": [162.5, 1221.3, 477.5, 1242.1]}, {"text": "(b) Change in Internal Controls. There have been no significant changes in internal controls or in other factors", "bbox": [162.5, 1275.4, 1112.3, 1296.2]}, {"text": "that could significantly affect internal controls subsequent to the date of the company’s most recent evaluation,", "bbox": [162.5, 1300.4, 1112.3, 1321.2]}, {"text": "including any corrective actions with regard to significant deficiencies or material weakness.", "bbox": [162.5, 1325.4, 937.1, 1346.2]}, {"